summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Moove fitness member app. All major pages and functionality working excellently including home page with featured content, search with filters and results, profile with stats/activity/favorites tabs, booking calendar with week/month views, and community feed with posts/polls/interactions.
passed_tests: Home page loads and displays featured workout and challenges
Search page shows recent searches, popular searches, and browse by category when empty
Search page filters work - clicking filter button shows Target Area, Category, Duration options
Search page shows results with tabs (All, Workouts, Challenges, Instructors) when searching
Profile page Stats tab shows minutes, classes, challenges count and streaks
Profile page Activity tab shows recent workout history
Profile page Favorites tab shows saved workouts
Book page shows week view calendar with class cards
Book page month view shows full monthly calendar
Book page booking functionality works (BOOK NOW â†’ CANCEL)
Community page shows completed workout cards, polls, and text posts
Community page poll voting functionality works with percentage results
Navigation between all pages works properly
All interactive elements are clickable and responsive
Mock data is loading and displaying correctly across all pages
